  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast, tuck into a continental buffet with hot options available too. For dinner you'll have a four-course meal from a set menu. Expect delicious Italian cuisine including some typical dishes from the Aosta Valley, followed by a post-dinner sweet wine, to be enjoyed at the dinner table. </p>
<p>The hotel also offers a packed lunch with a sandwich, sweet option, fruit and a bottle of water (payable locally, approx. €12 per person). As well as a daily selection of afternoon cakes from 4pm to 5pm (excludes drinks).</p>
<p>Most weekends a BBQ lunch is available (payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
