  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Hotel Guided Walks</strong></p>
<p>The hotel offers free hotel-run guided walks once or twice a week (weather permitting). The hotel staff  know the Aosta Valley like the back of their hand and are fantastic people to head into the mountains with.</p>
<p><strong>Hotel Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Live jazz in the garden during the first week of August from 5.30pm to 7.30pm </li>
<li>Wine tasting available on request (payable locally) </li>
<li>Discounted access to Champoluc's Monterosa Spa</li>
<li>Pilates class available (payable locally)</li>
<li>E-bikes for hire (bookable and payable locally, subject to availability)</li>
<li>Cosy lounge and bar area</li>
<li>Sky TV in public areas</li>
<li>One free local map provided per room</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Free parking </li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
